/ Stage 5 — the v1 wiring of file action handlers through Path.Authorize.
/ This test exercises the in-root happy path: file.save then file.read both
/ go through Authorize, both auto-grant (in-root), the round-trip works.
/ The out-of-root prompt/sign/store scenarios are exercised by the C# Stage 5
/ tests (PLang.Tests/App/FileSystem/Stage5MessagesEndToEndTests.cs) — the
/ PLang test runner can't easily set up real OS-out-of-root paths because
/ ValidatePath prefixes /-rooted paths with the test's RootDirectory.
- save 'fixture-content' to file 'fixture.txt'
- file.read fixture.txt, write to %content%
- assert %content% contains "fixture-content"
